AGI - Precautionary measure for three 19 years protagonists of a maxi rissa in Naples. The carabinieri of the Napoli Centro Company have performed an order issued by the partenopeo gip against three boys: for one there is the obligation of residence in the municipality of Naples while for the other two the prohibition of residence always in the Campania capital. The three inquiries took part, together with others in the process of identification and other minors for which they proceed separately, to the zuffa in the night of last May 26 in the historic center of Naples, a few steps from vico San Giovanni Maggiore, during which one of them extracted a knife but was struck by several fendents. During the fight, other boys also reported injuries including a passer, alien to the facts, judged healable in 12 days. The survey also developed thanks to the analysis of video surveillance systems in the area.
